"{\"uid\": \"atlantanewsfirst.com-2024-01-25-georgia-state-class-surprised-with-trip-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ATLANTA, Ga. (Atlanta News First) - A Georgia State University professor just struck gold twice actually, by giving her students a massive surprise.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\", \"score\": 0.999999999336751, \"rank\": 6.273283022910995e-10, \"text\": \"Georgia State University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a bit of a surprise Wednesday at Georgia State for a classroom full of unsuspecting law students.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 190, \"end\": 197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.9999966825887897, \"rank\": 1.9307763929167744e-06, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Georgia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the students are going to be so excited,\\\" said Mo Ivory, Creator, Founding Director and Professor of Practice of GSU's \\\"Legal Life of the Olympic Games\\\" course.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"score\": 0.9668681925314645, \"rank\": 0.03425049792795696, \"text\": \"Mo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\"}, {\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7782044226191225e-15, \"text\": \"GSU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_State_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ivory is at the head of the \\\"Legal Life of the Olympic Games\\\" class, teaching the ins and outs of international world-class events.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You might remember Ivory from a few months back.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She taught the legal life of Atlanta native Rick Ross, and then, by surprise, the boss himself showed up.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2396356780147863e-14, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\", \"score\": 0.9999999970123099, \"rank\": 2.9876808386314845e-09, \"text\": \"Rick Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rick never had a moment of pause to come.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I asked\\u2026 he said yes immediately,\\\" Ivory said.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The upcoming summer games are the focus now and as far as these students know, only one envelope has boarding passes to Paris for the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9910150196950023, \"rank\": 0.009066442108670296, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But thanks to some help from Delta Air Lines, everybody can draw an envelope.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delta_Air_Lines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Delta Air Lines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delta_Air_Lines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delta_Air_Lines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's an amazing experience to be able to provide this opportunity to my students,\\\" Ivory said.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's right, every single student will be crossing the pond to witness what for now is just lessons but will soon be life.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With them, the sky's the limit.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I was not expecting to go to Paris,\\\" one student said.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9910150196950023, \"rank\": 0.009066442108670296, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was stunned.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was crazy.\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Professor Mo is always pulling out all the stops in our classes, so I just love that they gave us tickets and a cute little beret to go with them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"score\": 0.9668681925316843, \"rank\": 0.03425049792795696, \"text\": \"Mo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"said another student.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, this next generation of attorneys will be getting some pretty cool hands-on experience before they get their hands on a law degree.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea that we can put the work that we are learning in the classroom into actual practice on the ground in Paris is just like a dream come true because, for students, that's how they are able to tie the concepts together,\\\" said Ivory.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9910150196950023, \"rank\": 0.009066442108670296, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are interested in sponsoring students for the Olympic Games, please contact Professor Mo Ivory atmivory@gsu.edu.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"score\": 0.9668681925316843, \"rank\": 0.03425049792795696, \"text\": \"Mo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More about the course  The \\\"Legal Life of the Olympic Games\\\" course was launched at Georgia State Law in 2019 by Professor of Practice Mo Ivory.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"score\": 0.9668681925316843, \"rank\": 0.03425049792795696, \"text\": \"Mo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molybdenum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, student participants have studied the legal life of Ludacris, Kandi Burruss, Steve Harvey and Rick Ross.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludacris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ludacris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludacris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ludacris\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kandi_Burruss\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kandi Burruss\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kandi_Burruss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kandi_Burruss\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Harvey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2157104007913634e-23, \"text\": \"Steve Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Harvey\"}, {\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\", \"score\": 0.9999999970123099, \"rank\": 2.9876808386314845e-09, \"text\": \"Rick Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rick_Ross\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The course is a part of the curriculum in the Center for Entertainment, Sports & Intellectual Property Law.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 WANF.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}]}"